{
  "draftPosts": [
    {
      "title": "How to build a hiring scorecard in 30 minutes",
      "memberId": "abce5218-72ad-4ab3-9b93-2ee0c0649248",
      "richContent": {
        "nodes": [
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Step-by-step guide to defining criteria, rating scales, and role-specific questions.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Building a hiring scorecard doesn't need to take days. With the right framework, you can create a robust evaluation tool in just 30 minutes.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Step 1: Define Your Must-Haves",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Start by listing 3-5 critical criteria that a candidate must demonstrate. These are non-negotiable skills or attributes for the role.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Step 2: Create a Rating Scale",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Use a simple 1-5 scale where each number has a clear definition. This removes subjectivity and ensures consistency across interviewers.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Step 3: Map Questions to Criteria",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "For each criterion, write 2-3 interview questions that help you assess it. Be specific and behavioural.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          }
        ]
      },
      "categoryIds": [],
      "tagIds": []
    },
    {
      "title": "Why async interviews save time (and improve candidate experience)",
      "memberId": "abce5218-72ad-4ab3-9b93-2ee0c0649248",
      "richContent": {
        "nodes": [
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Pre-recorded video questions reduce scheduling friction and give candidates flexibility.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Scheduling interviews is one of the biggest time drains in hiring. Async interviews solve this while improving the candidate experience.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "The Scheduling Problem",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Traditional interviews require coordinating calendars across time zones. This can delay hiring by weeks.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "How Async Interviews Work",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Candidates receive a link with pre-recorded questions. They record their answers on their own schedule. You review transcripts and videos when convenient.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Benefits for Candidates",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Candidates can complete interviews at times that work for them, reducing stress and showing them you respect their time.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          }
        ]
      },
      "categoryIds": [],
      "tagIds": []
    },
    {
      "title": "The 75th percentile rule for pre-screening senior candidates",
      "memberId": "abce5218-72ad-4ab3-9b93-2ee0c0649248",
      "richContent": {
        "nodes": [
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Only advance candidates who score in the top 25% of the pool to reduce interview noise.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "For senior roles, you can't afford to waste time interviewing marginal candidates. The 75th percentile rule helps you focus on only the best.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "What It Means",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "After initial screening, only candidates who score in the top 25% of your candidate pool move to final interviews. Everyone else gets a polite rejection.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Why It Works",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "This rule forces you to compare candidates against each other, not against an abstract standard. It ensures you only spend time on genuinely strong performers.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "How to Apply It",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Score all candidates using your scorecard. Rank them. Draw a line at the 75th percentile. Only candidates above that line advance.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          }
        ]
      },
      "categoryIds": [],
      "tagIds": []
    },
    {
      "title": "Five email outreach templates that get replies",
      "memberId": "abce5218-72ad-4ab3-9b93-2ee0c0649248",
      "richContent": {
        "nodes": [
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Proven sequences for engaging passive candidates with personalised messaging.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Most outreach emails get ignored. These five templates have proven reply rates above 30%.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Template 1: The Problem-Solution Opener",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Start with a problem you know they face, then introduce your role as the solution.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Template 2: The Mutual Connection",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Reference someone you both know or a shared interest to build immediate credibility.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Template 3: The Specific Compliment",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Mention something specific they've built or written. Shows you've done research.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          }
        ]
      },
      "categoryIds": [],
      "tagIds": []
    },
    {
      "title": "How to set up an ATS in Notion (free template)",
      "memberId": "abce5218-72ad-4ab3-9b93-2ee0c0649248",
      "richContent": {
        "nodes": [
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Lightweight candidate tracking for small teams, no expensive software required.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "You don't need expensive ATS software to track candidates effectively. Notion provides everything you need.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Database Structure",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Create a database with columns for candidate name, role, stage, scorecard rating, interview notes, and next action.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
