    {
      "title": "Three signs your hiring process is broken (and how to fix it)",
      "memberId": "abce5218-72ad-4ab3-9b93-2ee0c0649248",
      "richContent": {
        "nodes": [
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Inconsistent pipelines, slow response times, and ghosting candidates.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Most small teams don't realise their hiring process is broken until it's too late. Here are three warning signs.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Sign 1: Inconsistent Pipeline Volume",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Some months you have 20 candidates, other months zero. This signals you're relying on luck, not a repeatable system. Fix: Set up consistent outreach and social posting schedules.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Sign 2: Response Time Over 48 Hours",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "If candidates wait more than two days for a response, you're losing good people to faster competitors. Fix: Implement auto-replies and set SLAs for stage transitions.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Sign 3: High Candidate Ghosting Rate",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "If more than 30% of candidates stop responding after initial contact, your process is too slow or unclear. Fix: Shorten time to first interview and set clear expectations upfront.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          }
        ]
      },
      "categoryIds": [],
      "tagIds": []
    },
    {
      "title": "How to write a role intake brief that actually works",
      "memberId": "abce5218-72ad-4ab3-9b93-2ee0c0649248",
      "richContent": {
        "nodes": [
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Define success criteria, must-haves vs. nice-to-haves, and interview focus areas.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "A good role intake brief is the foundation of effective hiring. Here's how to write one that guides your entire process.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Define Success in 90 Days",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "What does success look like three months after hire? Be specific about deliverables, not vague about attributes.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Separate Must-Haves from Nice-to-Haves",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Most teams list 15 requirements when only three truly matter. Force yourself to identify the 3-5 non-negotiables.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Map Interview Focus Areas",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "For each must-have criterion, define which interview stage will assess it and what evidence you're looking for.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          }
        ]
      },
      "categoryIds": [],
      "tagIds": []
    },
    {
      "title": "Why posting jobs on LinkedIn isn't enough",
      "memberId": "abce5218-72ad-4ab3-9b93-2ee0c0649248",
      "richContent": {
        "nodes": [
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Active outreach, social distribution, and referral networks drive better candidate quality.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Posting a job and waiting for applications is a passive strategy. The best candidates aren't actively looking.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "The Problem with Job Boards",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Job boards attract active job seekers, who are often less qualified or more desperate than passive candidates who are happy in their current role.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Active Outreach Wins",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Email outreach to passive candidates in adjacent roles yields higher quality and better cultural fit. It takes more work, but the ROI is worth it.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Social Distribution Matters",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Posting on Twitter, in niche Slack communities, and on founder networks gets your role in front of people who aren't checking LinkedIn.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          }
        ]
      },
      "categoryIds": [],
      "tagIds": []
    },
    {
      "title": "How to run a 30-minute pre-screen interview",
      "memberId": "abce5218-72ad-4ab3-9b93-2ee0c0649248",
      "richContent": {
        "nodes": [
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Question framework, scorecard alignment, and what to look for in senior candidates.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "A tight 30-minute pre-screen filters out weak candidates before you invest in longer interviews. Here's the structure.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "First 5 Minutes: Context Setting",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Briefly explain the role, company stage, and what success looks like. This gives candidates context for their answers.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Next 20 Minutes: Scorecard Questions",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Ask two to three questions per scorecard criterion. Listen for specificity, ownership, and outcomes. Take notes using your rating scale.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          },
          {
            "type": "HEADING",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Final 5 Minutes: Candidate Questions",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "headingData": {
              "level": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "PARAGRAPH",
            "nodes": [{
              "type": "TEXT",
              "textData": {
                "text": "Let them ask questions. The quality of their questions reveals how much they've thought about the role.",
                "decorations": []
              }
            }],
            "paragraphData": {}
          }
        ]
      },
      "categoryIds": [],
      "tagIds": []
    }
  ],
  "returnEntity": true
}
